comments.content: If you ask me, if it is actually a font, it would take longer to find it, set it, and convert to outlines than it would to build it from scratch. Ought to take about half an hour, tops.

I first thought it would be a free font named ' [Seeds](http://web.archive.org/web/20050518052601/http:/www.dafont.com/en/search.php?nq=1&q=seeds)', by Matt Perkins, but, nope, its not..   
 [http://www.dafont.com/en/search.php?nq=1&q=seeds](http://web.archive.org/web/20050518052601/http:/www.dafont.com/en/search.php?nq=1&q=seeds)   
 _Sorry that I couldnt help either.._
Thanks for your time David. It's done.
